name: Twilight Furniture
description: a little journal with failed & test prints from the time I started out making darkroom prints at home. I used paper from the 1960s, hence the creamy tone of it. You'll see some glimpses of Berlin and Hamburg, read some words stolen from This Heat (title), Leonard Cohen (first text) & Pink Floyd (last text), & see a few exposed body parts. :: {2012} :: @annaxmalina :: annamalina.com
